# .forceignore - Exclude files from deployment
#
# Standard exclusions for smart-deployment project

# Package directories
**/.forceignore
**/.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/.hg
**/.svn
**/.git
**/node_modules/**
**/.cache

# LWC and Aura (not in this project)
**/*.spec.js
**/*.test.js
**/__tests__/**

# Source maps
**/*.map

# Build output
**/dist/**
**/lib/**
**/.github/**

# Development files
**/coverage/**
**/test/**
**/.tmp/**
**/*.log

# IDE files
**/.vscode/**
**/.idea/**

